    Aracnia looked over Cyberclaw with a bit of tension. A new bot might mean 
trouble.....but she needed an escourt and this would be an excellent test. 
"Welcome Cyber Claw, and thank you for Rat Trap. In the mean time I want you 
to come with me to Kitkats base. It wil lgive us a chance to....lets 
say...bond."

    Inferno turned to Drillbit, and gave a long laugh. "Foolish traitor! You 
will be destroyed!" Inferno said and jumped into action and taking to the sky.
